description.en: Healing Plus provides a platform for systematic medical services after storing members' health information on the blockchain and sharing them. The main project is Yunohana Hot Spring. If the user holds the Token, it can be used at any Yunohana Hot Spring in the whole of Korea, and related health products can also be purchased. In addition, all systems are based on blockchain technology. With the increase of franchise stores across the country, the value of Healing Plus Token (HP) is also rising.
